## SESSION START RITUAL

1. Read this CLAUDE.md (you are reading it now)
2. Read docs/SESSION_LOG.md — check for pending items
3. Read VALIDATION_LOG.md — check for open decisions
4. Run: npx tsc --noEmit — verify clean state
5. Post to Slack #nm-ceo ([MASKED_CHANNEL_ID]): "SESSION STARTED — Gate: G6. Pending: [X items]."
6. Announce to PD: "Session ready. Gate: G6. Pending: [X items]."

